            "title": "ShokaX 安裝教學",
            "date_published": "2024-08-02T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"介紹\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#介紹\">#</a> 介紹</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Hexo 是一個部落格框架，可以生成靜態網頁。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Shoka</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>是一個 Hexo 主題，Shoka 取的名字是<code>書架</code>，是一個為了閱讀筆記而生的主題，<br />\n相關介紹可以參考作者網站：<a href=\"https://shoka.lostyu.me/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/\">https://shoka.lostyu.me/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/</a><br />\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"item\" title=\"霜月琉璃\" style=\"--block-color:#e9546b;\"><a href=\"https://shoka.lostyu.me\" class=\"image\" data-background-image=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amehime/shoka@latest/images/avatar.jpg\"></a>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n        <a href=\"https://shoka.lostyu.me\" class=\"title\">優萌初華</a>\n        <p class=\"desc\">Shoka作者</p>\n        </div></div></div></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/shokaX/shokaAuthor.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"80%\" /><br />\nShoka 作者於<a href=\"https://shoka.lostyu.me/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/\">部落格底下的留言中的回覆</a>，<br />\n該項目可能不再更新，Github 上最後的 Commit 日期是<a href=\"https://github.com/amehime/hexo-theme-shoka\">2021/10/03</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>ShokaX</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/theme-shoka-x/hexo-theme-shokaX\">https://github.com/theme-shoka-x/hexo-theme-shokaX</a><br />\nShokaX 是 Shoka 的精神續作，<br />\n原先 Shoka 使用了 JavaScript + Native + Nunjucks 的技術，<br />\n而 ShokaX 則使用了 TypeScript + Vue 3 + Pug 的技術搭配，<br />\n並新增了一些功能。</p>\n<h1 id=\"安裝\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#安裝\">#</a> 安裝</h1>\n<div class=\"note info\">\n<p>shokaX-CLI 已棄用，詳情: <a href=\"https://github.com/theme-shoka-x/shokaX-CLI\">https://github.com/theme-shoka-x/shokaX-CLI</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>安裝文檔: <a href=\"https://docs-hexo.shokax.top/getting-started/\">https://docs-hexo.shokax.top/getting-started/</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>使用 shokaX can<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/theme-shoka-x/shokax-can\">https://github.com/theme-shoka-x/shokax-can</a></li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">git</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> clone</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> https://github.com/theme-shoka-x/shokax-can</span><span style=\"color:#A65E2B;--shiki-dark:#C99076\"> --depth=1</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">cd</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> shokax-can</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">pnpm</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> install</span></span></code></pre>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>依說明文檔進行配置<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.kaitaku.xyz/guide/config.html\">https://docs.kaitaku.xyz/guide/config.html</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>啟動 hexo server</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">hexo</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> s</span><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"> # 如果報錯更換為 pnpm dlx hexo s</span></span></code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"撰寫第一篇文章\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#撰寫第一篇文章\">#</a> 撰寫第一篇文章</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>在<code>source/_posts</code>資料夾下新增一個<code>md</code>檔案，例如：<code>first.md</code>。</li>\n<li>在檔案內容中新增一些內容，例如：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-md\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">title: 第一篇文章</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">date: 2024-04-24</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">tags: ShokaX</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1C6B48;--shiki-light-font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#4D9375;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\">---</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-light-font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#666666;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\">#</span><span style=\"color:#1C6B48;--shiki-light-font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#4D9375;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\"> 第一篇文章</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">這是內容</span></span></code></pre>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>可以看到第一篇文章了。<br />\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/shokaX/firstpost.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"80%\" /></li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"seo-設置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#seo-設置\">#</a> SEO 設置</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>安裝 hexo-generator-sitemap</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">npm</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> hexo-generator-sitemap</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> </span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console\">Google SEO</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://analytics.google.com/\">Google Analytics</a></li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">seo</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">  google</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"> # 填入資訊</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">visitor</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">  googleAnalytics</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"> # 填入資訊</span></span></code></pre>\n",
